Position Code Expression (For Variable: PositionCode)

Code snippet
first(match(string(outputs('EmailBody')), '(?<=Position\s+Title:\s*.*?\()\d{8}'))
2. Link Expression (For Variable: ApprovalLink)

Code snippet
first(match(string(outputs('EmailBody')), '(?i)(?<=Please\s+click\s+<a\s+href=")([^"]+)(?=">here)'))
